degrees in the car, officials said. The child's body temperature
was 108 degrees when he was taken to Baptist Medical Center.
   Mrs. Blok said she she left the boy the the car when she went to
visit a friend because he was asleep.
   Wiggins ordered Mrs. Blok to report to prison Monday.
